                span(class="font-normal text-xs md:text-base sm:text-xs leading-tight text-gray-60 md:text-white text-center xs:-mx-2")
                    | Рекомендуемая оплата
                span(class="font-normal md:font-bold text-xs md:text-2xl sm:text-xl leading-tight text-red-70 md:text-white")
                    | #{sum} ₴
